## üé® CSS Specific

```json
"css": {
  "formatter": {
    "indentStyle": "tab",
    "indentWidth": 2,
    "lineEnding": "lf",
    "lineWidth": 80,
    "quoteStyle": "double"
  },
  "parser": {
    "allowWrongLineComments": true,
    "cssModules": true
  }
}
```

* Tab-indented with double quotes.
* Supports CSS Modules.
* Allows malformed line comments during parse.

