## üìù JSON Specific

```json
"json": {
  "formatter": {
    "enabled": true,
    "indentStyle": "tab",
    "indentWidth": 2,
    "lineEnding": "lf",
    "lineWidth": 80,
    "trailingCommas": "none"
  },
  "linter": { "enabled": true },
  "parser": {
    "allowComments": false,
    "allowTrailingCommas": false
  }
}
```

* Tab-indented JSON, no trailing commas.
* Comments and trailing commas in source JSON are disallowed.

